# 🧼 Handwashing & Death Rate Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes the impact of handwashing on death rates, inspired by historical medical data. It demonstrates how a simple hygiene practice significantly reduced mortality rates in hospitals.

The analysis highlights the importance of data in uncovering life-saving insights.

---

## 🎯 Objective

* Analyze death rates before and after handwashing was introduced
* Understand trends in mortality over time
* Visualize the effectiveness of hygiene practices
* Derive meaningful insights from historical data

---

## 📂 Dataset

The dataset includes:

* Number of births
* Number of deaths
* Death rate (%)
* Timeline (monthly/yearly data)

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

* Python 🐍
* Pandas
* NumPy
* Matplotlib
* Seaborn
* Jupyter Notebook

---

## 🔍 Steps Performed

### 1. Data Loading

* Imported dataset into Pandas DataFrame
* Checked structure and cleaned data

### 2. Data Cleaning

* Handled missing/null values
* Converted date columns into proper datetime format

### 3. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

* Calculated death rates
* Compared trends before and after handwashing
* Grouped data for better analysis

### 4. Data Visualization

* 📈 Line Plot → Death rate over time
* 📊 Bar Chart → Before vs After comparison
* 📉 Trend Analysis → Impact visualization

---

## 📊 Key Insights

* Introduction of handwashing drastically reduced death rates
* Clear downward trend in mortality after hygiene practices
* Data strongly supports the importance of sanitation in healthcare

